{"type":"message","id":"74157548","parentId":"9e775ebf","timestamp":"2026-06-23T16:00:06.097Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:500a1a24-2ac8-4b36-837a-43d940722302 Noticias IA y Temperatura Goicoechea] Crea un reporte matutino especializado para Kenneth (IA Engineer en formación). ENFOQUE: 1. TEMPERATURA de Goicoechea, CR. 2. NOTICIAS TÉCNICAS PARA IA ENGINEERS, con énfasis en: - Herramientas para desarrolladores full-stack (frontend + IA) - APIs y bibliotecas de IA para TypeScript/JavaScript - Integración de IA con frontend moderno (React, Vue, Tailwind) - Recursos de aprendizaje práctico para IA Engineering - Frameworks y herramientas accesibles para desarrolladores web 3. ANÁLISIO PRÁCTICO: Cómo aplicar las noticias en proyectos de aprendizaje. 4. RECOMENDACIÓN DIARIA: Una herramienta, tutorial o recurso para practicar. Formato: Breve, práctico, enfocado en aprendizaje activo.\nCurrent time: Tuesday, June 23rd, 2026 - 4:00 PM (UTC)\nReference UTC: 2026-06-23 16:00 UTC\n\nUse the message tool if you need to notify the user directly for the current chat. If you do not send directly, your final plain-text reply will be delivered automatically."}],"timestamp":1782230406094}}
{"type":"message","id":"9828fb80","parentId":"74157548","timestamp":"2026-06-23T16:00:48.582Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Entiendo que necesitas crear un reporte matutino especializado para Kenneth (IA Engineer en formación). Voy a buscar la información requerida:\n\n1. Temperatura de Goicoechea, Costa Rica\n2. Noticias técnicas para IA Engineers\n3. Análisis práctico y recomendación\n\nPrimero, buscaré el clima actual en Goicoechea.\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"dfaa9744b3cb4806a01f09ab881f5ab4","name":"composio__COMPOSIO_SEARCH_TOOLS","arguments":{"queries":[{"use_case":"get current weather information for a specific location"}],"session":{"generate_id":true}},"partialArgs":"{\"queries\": [{\"use_case\": \"get current weather information for a specific location\"}], \"session\": {\"generate_id\": true}}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"litellm","model":"online/openrouter/deepseek/deepseek-v3.2","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782230406102,"responseId":"gen-1782230406-Co0cCmUIyrlxEcQSzZuB"}}
{"type":"message","id":"37473e84","parentId":"9828fb80","timestamp":"2026-06-23T16:00:51.034Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"dfaa9744b3cb4806a01f09ab881f5ab4","toolName":"composio__COMPOSIO_SEARCH_TOOLS","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\"data\":{\"results\":[{\"index\":1,\"use_case\":\"get current weather information for a specific location\",\"execution_guidance\":\"IMPORTANT: Follow the recommended plan below. Extract steps before execution, adapt to your current context, execute sequentially with current_step parameter, and check known pitfalls to avoid errors.\",\"recommended_plan_steps\":[\"[Required] [Step]: Fetch current conditions per location using WEATHERMAP_WEATHER (capture temperature/feels-like, condition summary, wind, humidity, and any returned alerts).\",\"[Required] [Fallback]: If WEATHERMAP_WEATHER returns 404/ambiguous match, resolve the place using WEATHERMAP_GEOCODE_LOCATION (pick best candidate), then retry WEATHERMAP_WEATHER with the canonical location.\",\"[Optional (if you need stable coordinates or names collide)] [Prerequisite]: Get latitude/longitude using OPENWEATHER_API_GET_GEOCODING_DIRECT (reuse coords across calls).\",\"[Optional (if WEATHERMAP_WEATHER is unavailable or you want a second source)] [Next Step]: Retrieve current weather using OPENWEATHER_API_GET_CURRENT_WEATHER (use exactly one identifier: q OR id OR zip OR lat+lon; align units/lang).\",\"[Optional (if you queried both sources)] [Next Step]: Cross-check key fields (temp/conditions/wind/alerts) between WEATHERMAP_WEATHER and OPENWEATHER_API_GET_CURRENT_WEATHER and flag discrepancies by source.\",\"[Required] [Next Step]: Present consolidated conditions and any alerts (label source); convert temperatures to °C/°F and render timestamps in local time using the response timezone offset when available.\"],\"known_pitfalls\":[\"[WEATHERMAP_GEOCODE_LOCATION] Multiple candidates are common; selecting the wrong region can return plausible but incorrect weather.\",\"[OPENWEATHER_API_GET_CURRENT_WEATHER] Must pass exactly one of q/id/zip/lat+lon per call; mixing identifiers can error or create ambiguity.\",\"[WEATHERMAP_WEATHER] Some fields (e.g., visibility/pressure/clouds) may be absent; handle missing keys gracefully.\",\"[WEATHERMAP_WEATHER] Alerts are not guaranteed even in severe conditions; treat missing alerts as “none returned by API,” not “none exist.”\"],\"difficulty\":\"easy\",\"primary_tool_slugs\":[\"WEATHERMAP_WEATHER\"],\"related_tool_slugs\":[\"WEATHERMAP_GEOCODE_LOCATION\",\"OPENWEATHER_API_GET_GEOCODING_DIRECT\",\"OPENWEATHER_API_GET_CURRENT_WEATHER\"],\"toolkits\":[\"openweather_api\",\"weathermap\"],\"plan_id\":\"0fc54eba8d074380ba91803efc71d410\"}],\"toolkit_connection_statuses\":[{\"toolkit\":\"openweather_api\",\"description\":\"Provides access to current weather data, forecasts, and historical weather data for any location worldwide.\",\"has_active_connection\":false,\"status_message\":\"No Active connection for toolkit=openweather_api. You MUST call COMPOSIO_MANAGE_CONNECTIONS (toolkit=\\\"openweather_api\\\") to create a connection BEFORE executing any openweather_api tools.\"},{\"toolkit\":\"weathermap\",\"description\":\"WeatherMap provides visual weather data, forecasts, and mappings, helping users understand climate patterns or track severe weather conditions\",\"has_active_connection\":true,\"status_message\":\"This toolkit does not require authentication. Tools are ready to use.\"}],\"tool_schemas\":{\"WEATHERMAP_WEATHER\":{\"toolkit\":\"WEATHERMAP\",\"tool_slug\":\"WEATHERMAP_WEATHER\",\"description\":\"Tool for querying the OpenWeatherMap API. Returns current weather conditions only — no UV index, AQI, or official alerts. Timestamps are in UTC; apply the timezone offset field before grouping by local day.\",\"input_schema\":{\"type\":\"object\",\"required\":[\"location\"],\"properties\":{\"location\":{\"type\":\"string\",\"examples\":[\"London,GB\",\"Redding,CA,US\",\"London\",\"New York\",\"Tokyo\"],\"description\":\"A real city name (e.g., 'London', 'New York', 'Tokyo'). MUST be an actual city name - NOT a placeholder like 'your location', 'current location', or 'my location'. City names must be in English/Latin characters only. You may optionally append a country code (e.g., 'London,GB'). For US cities with state abbreviations, use the 3-part format 'City,StateCode,US' (e.g., 'Redding,CA,US', 'Portland,OR,US') - the 2-part format 'City,StateCode' will be interpreted as a country code (e.g., 'CA' = Canada, not California). If a 'city not found' error occurs, retry with a simpler string (e.g., drop state code, use just 'City' or 'City,CountryCode'). Small or remote locations may return no data; handle gracefully rather than retrying indefinitely.\"}}},\"hasFullSchema\":true},\"WEATHERMAP_GEOCODE_LOCATION\":{\"toolkit\":\"WEATHERMAP\",\"tool_slug\":\"WEATHERMAP_GEOCODE_LOCATION\",\"description\":\"Tool to resolve a human place name into canonical lat/lon coordinates using OpenWeather Geocoding API. Use when you need to convert location strings (city names, addresses) into coordinates for weather forecasts or other location-based queries. Returns up to 5 candidate matches; the first result is typically the most relevant.\",\"input_schema\":{\"type\":\"object\",\"required\":[\"q\"],\"properties\":{\"q\":{\"type\":\"string\",\"examples\":[\"Rarotonga,CK\",\"London,GB\",\"Austin,TX,US\",\"New York\",\"Tokyo,JP\"],\"description\":\"Location query string in format 'city' or 'city,country_code' or 'city,state,country_code'. For US locations, you can include state code (e.g., 'Austin,TX,US'). Use ISO 3166 country codes (e.g., 'London,GB', 'Paris,FR'). The API supports 200,000+ registered locations.\"},\"limit\":{\"type\":\"integer\",\"default\":5,\"maximum\":5,\"minimum\":1,\"examples\":[1,3,5],\"description\":\"Maximum number of location matches to return (1-5). Use this to limit results when multiple locations share the same name. Default is 5.\"}}},\"hasFullSchema\":true},\"OPENWEATHER_API_GET_GEOCODING_DIRECT\":{\"toolkit\":\"OPENWEATHER_API\",\"tool_slug\":\"OPENWEATHER_API_GET_GEOCODING_DIRECT\",\"description\":\"Tool to convert a location name into geographic coordinates. Use when you need latitude and longitude for a given location after confirming the precise name.\",\"input_schema\":{\"type\":\"object\",\"required\":[\"q\"],\"properties\":{\"q\":{\"type\":\"string\",\"examples\":[\"London,UK\"],\"description\":\"Location query including city name, state code and country code separated by commas (e.g., 'London,UK'). Ambiguous queries can return multiple mismatched locations; use the full three-part format 'city,state_code,country_code' (e.g., 'Springfield,IL,US') and verify the returned country/region before using coordinates downstream.\"},\"limit\":{\"type\":\"integer\",\"default\":5,\"maximum\":5,\"minimum\":1,\"examples\":[5],\"description\":\"Number of results to return (1 to 5). Defaults to 5. Use 1 only for unambiguous locations; for ambiguous queries review all returned results to select the correct match.\"}}},\"hasFullSchema\":true},\"OPENWEATHER_API_GET_CURRENT_WEATHER\":{\"toolkit\":\"OPENWEATHER_API\",\"tool_slug\":\"OPENWEATHER_API_GET_CURRENT_WEATHER\",\"description\":\"Tool to retrieve current weather data for a location. Use when you need up-to-the-minute weather inf...\",\"hasFullSchema\":false,\"schemaRef\":{\"tool\":\"COMPOSIO_GET_TOOL_SCHEMAS\",\"args\":{\"tool_slugs\":[\"OPENWEATHER_API_GET_CURRENT_WEATHER\"]}}}},\"time_info\":{\"current_time_utc\":\"2026-06-23T16:00:50.924Z\",\"current_time_utc_epoch_seconds\":1782230450,\"message\":\"\\n          - This is time in UTC timezone. Get timezone from user if you needed.\\n          - Always use this time info to construct parameters for tool calls appropriately even when the tool call requires relative times like 'last week', 'last 24 hours', 'today', 'tomorrow' etc.\\n          - Do not hallucinate the time or timezone by yourself.\\n        \"},\"session\":{\"id\":\"ball\",\"generate_id\":true,\"instructions\":\"REQUIRED: Pass session_id \\\"ball\\\" in ALL subsequent meta tool calls for this workflow.\"},\"next_steps_guidance\":[\"1) You may call COMPOSIO_MANAGE_CONNECTIONS: Some toolkits lack active connections\",\"2) Extract validated plan steps returned above, acknowledge each step, then execute sequentially updating current_step parameter. Check pitfalls during execution.\"],\"success\":true,\"error\":null},\"error\":null,\"log_id\":\"log_IFyOZneZlppa\",\"successful\":true}"}],"details":{"mcpServer":"composio","mcpTool":"COMPOSIO_SEARCH_TOOLS"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1782230451032}}
