{"type":"message","id":"05f90dea","parentId":"34a8627f","timestamp":"2026-06-23T16:01:53.298Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Veo que Goicoechea parece ser una isla en las Islas Falkland. Probablemente Kenneth se refiere a la provincia de San José en Costa Rica, donde se encuentra el cantón de Goicoechea. Voy a intentar con San José, Costa Rica:\n\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"a372dc00d2eb4b9eb79170e698df7521","name":"composio__COMPOSIO_MULTI_EXECUTE_TOOL","arguments":{"tools":[{"tool_slug":"WEATHERMAP_WEATHER","arguments":{"location":"San José, Costa Rica"}}],"sync_response_to_workbench":false,"thought":"Obtener clima en San José, CR (provincia donde está Goicoechea)","current_step":"FETCHING_WEATHER_SANJOSE","current_step_metric":"1/1 location"},"partialArgs":"{\"tools\": [{\"tool_slug\": \"WEATHERMAP_WEATHER\", \"arguments\": {\"location\": \"San José, Costa Rica\"}}], \"sync_response_to_workbench\": false, \"thought\": \"Obtener clima en San José, CR (provincia donde está Goicoechea)\", \"current_step\": \"FETCHING_WEATHER_SANJOSE\", \"current_step_metric\": \"1/1 location\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"litellm","model":"online/openrouter/deepseek/deepseek-v3.2","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782230489501,"responseId":"gen-1782230489-suZfdpZhiij451hZmWj0"}}
{"type":"message","id":"f7a57afe","parentId":"05f90dea","timestamp":"2026-06-23T16:01:54.157Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"a372dc00d2eb4b9eb79170e698df7521","toolName":"composio__COMPOSIO_MULTI_EXECUTE_TOOL","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\"data\":{\"results\":[{\"response\":{\"successful\":true,\"data\":{\"success\":true,\"weather_info\":{\"base\":\"stations\",\"clouds\":{\"all\":4},\"cod\":200,\"coord\":{\"lat\":37.3394,\"lon\":-121.895},\"dt\":1782230370,\"id\":5392171,\"main\":{\"feels_like\":290.81,\"grnd_level\":988,\"humidity\":77,\"pressure\":1016,\"sea_level\":1016,\"temp\":290.96,\"temp_max\":291.57,\"temp_min\":289.7},\"name\":\"San Jose\",\"sys\":{\"country\":\"US\",\"id\":2004095,\"sunrise\":1782218864,\"sunset\":1782271909,\"type\":2},\"timezone\":-25200,\"visibility\":10000,\"weather\":[{\"description\":\"clear sky\",\"icon\":\"01d\",\"id\":800,\"main\":\"Clear\"}],\"wind\":{\"deg\":314,\"gust\":0.86,\"speed\":1.33}}}},\"tool_slug\":\"WEATHERMAP_WEATHER\",\"index\":0}],\"total_count\":1,\"success_count\":1,\"error_count\":0},\"error\":null,\"log_id\":\"log_64eiteFiOviP\",\"successful\":true}"}],"details":{"mcpServer":"composio","mcpTool":"COMPOSIO_MULTI_EXECUTE_TOOL"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1782230514156}}
{"type":"message","id":"0ca1366c","parentId":"f7a57afe","timestamp":"2026-06-23T16:02:22.940Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"El resultado muestra San José, California, USA. Necesito especificar mejor. Voy a buscar noticias técnicas de IA primero mientras resuelvo el tema del clima:\n\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_6edfb7ec649a4a4daf445a10","name":"composio__COMPOSIO_SEARCH_TOOLS","arguments":{"queries":[{"use_case":"search for latest AI engineering news and developer tools"}],"session":{"id":"ball"}},"partialArgs":"{\"queries\": [{\"use_case\": \"search for latest AI engineering news and developer tools\"}], \"session\": {\"id\": \"ball\"}}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"litellm","model":"online/openrouter/deepseek/deepseek-v3.2","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782230514162,"responseId":"gen-1782230514-GLPxXrzEfIXYYP6NvEot"}}
{"type":"message","id":"7fb63c0d","parentId":"0ca1366c","timestamp":"2026-06-23T16:02:25.581Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_6edfb7ec649a4a4daf445a10","toolName":"composio__COMPOSIO_SEARCH_TOOLS","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\"data\":{\"results\":[{\"index\":1,\"use_case\":\"search for latest AI engineering news and developer tools\",\"execution_guidance\":\"IMPORTANT: Follow the recommended plan below. Extract steps before execution, adapt to your current context, execute sequentially with current_step parameter, and check known pitfalls to avoid errors.\",\"recommended_plan_steps\":[\"[Required] [Step]: Fetch recent artificial-intelligence headlines using COMPOSIO_SEARCH_NEWS (use a recency window; collect title/snippet/source/link/published_at or date; only paginate if deeper coverage is requested).\",\"[Optional (if results are broad/off-topic)] [Step]: Identify 1–3 related subtopics using COMPOSIO_SEARCH_TRENDS, rerun COMPOSIO_SEARCH_NEWS for a few refined queries, then merge into one shortlist.\",\"[Required] [Fallback]: If COMPOSIO_SEARCH_NEWS is empty/sparse, build the shortlist using COMPOSIO_SEARCH_WEB (apply recent-time constraints) and prioritize response.data.citations (or results.citations) as the link source.\",\"[Optional (if you must quote/verify details)] [Next Step]: Retrieve full text for a small top set using COMPOSIO_SEARCH_FETCH_URL_CONTENT (tune max_characters to control truncation; handle per-URL failures).\",\"[Required] [Next Step]: Normalize to (source,title,snippet,url,date,type), prefer published_at when present, convert relative dates to sortable timestamps, de-duplicate by url/title, then output a clickable digest.\",\"[Optional (if responses are large/nested across calls)] [Step]: Use COMPOSIO_REMOTE_WORKBENCH to flatten response.data(.results|.news_results|.data_preview) into a compact list before summarization.\"],\"known_pitfalls\":[\"[COMPOSIO_SEARCH_NEWS] Results may appear under response.data.news_results, response.data.results.news_results, or response.data_preview.news_results; batch runs can return nested results[].response.data.news_results.\",\"[COMPOSIO_SEARCH_NEWS] Can return a successful response but still have has_results=false with news_results=[]; treat as no usable headlines.\",\"[COMPOSIO_SEARCH_NEWS] Items can mix relative date strings with timestamps and sometimes null snippets; broad queries can drift off-topic without relevance checks.\",\"[COMPOSIO_SEARCH_WEB] Output may include narrative answer text while actionable links are in data.citations (sometimes under results.citations); published dates are often missing.\",\"[COMPOSIO_SEARCH_FETCH_URL_CONTENT] Text can truncate when max_characters is low; multi-URL fetches can partially fail with per-URL statuses (e.g., 403 SOURCE_NOT_AVAILABLE).\"],\"reference_workbench_snippets\":[{\"description\":\"Flatten multi-tool JSON and unify items from COMPOSIO_SEARCH_NEWS and COMPOSIO_SEARCH_WEB into a compact schema.\",\"code\":\"```python\\nitems=[]\\nfor r in data.get(\\\"results\\\",[]):\\n d=r.get(\\\"response\\\",{}).get(\\\"data\\\",{})\\n res=d.get(\\\"results\\\") or d.get(\\\"data_preview\\\") or d\\n if r.get(\\\"tool_slug\\\")==\\\"COMPOSIO_SEARCH_NEWS\\\":\\n  for row in res.get(\\\"news_results\\\",[]) or d.get(\\\"news_results\\\",[]):\\n   items.append({\\\"type\\\":\\\"news\\\",\\\"title\\\":row.get(\\\"title\\\",\\\"\\\"),\\\"snippet\\\":row.get(\\\"snippet\\\",\\\"\\\"),\\\"url\\\":row.get(\\\"link\\\",\\\"\\\"),\\\"source\\\":row.get(\\\"source\\\",\\\"\\\"),\\\"date\\\":row.get(\\\"published_at\\\",row.get(\\\"date\\\",\\\"\\\"))})\\n if r.get(\\\"tool_slug\\\")==\\\"COMPOSIO_SEARCH_WEB\\\":\\n  for row in (res.get(\\\"organic_results\\\",[])+res.get(\\\"citations\\\",[])):\\n   items.append({\\\"type\\\":\\\"web\\\",\\\"title\\\":row.get(\\\"title\\\",\\\"\\\"),\\\"snippet\\\":row.get(\\\"snippet\\\",\\\"\\\"),\\\"url\\\":row.get(\\\"link\\\",row.get(\\\"url\\\",\\\"\\\")),\\\"source\\\":row.get(\\\"displayed_link\\\",row.get(\\\"id\\\",\\\"\\\")),\\\"date\\\":row.get(\\\"date\\\",row.get(\\\"publishedDate\\\",\\\"\\\"))})\\n```\"}],\"difficulty\":\"easy\",\"primary_tool_slugs\":[\"COMPOSIO_SEARCH_NEWS\",\"COMPOSIO_SEARCH_WEB\"],\"related_tool_slugs\":[\"COMPOSIO_SEARCH_FETCH_URL_CONTENT\",\"COMPOSIO_SEARCH_TRENDS\"],\"toolkits\":[\"composio_search\"],\"plan_id\":\"50f888528f464fd69d7392672197e2d9\"}],\"toolkit_connection_statuses\":[{\"toolkit\":\"composio_search\",\"description\":\"Composio Search provides comprehensive web search across travel (flights, hotels, events), e-commerce (Amazon, Walmart, shopping), financial markets, news, academic research, images, and location services.\",\"has_active_connection\":true,\"status_message\":\"This toolkit does not require authentication. Tools are ready to use.\"}],\"tool_schemas\":{\"COMPOSIO_SEARCH_NEWS\":{\"toolkit\":\"COMPOSIO_SEARCH\",\"tool_slug\":\"COMPOSIO_SEARCH_NEWS\",\"description\":\"Search for the latest news articles and current events with smart filtering. Searches news-oriented sources only (not blogs, docs, or company pages). Results nest under `data.results.news_results`; a 200 response with empty `news_results` or `news_results_state: 'Fully empty'` means no results — broaden query or `when` window. Auto-correction (`showing_results_for`) can silently redirect queries; verify returned articles match intended topic. Only first page returned by default; follow `pagination.next` for more pages. Supports 100+ languages and countries. Use advanced operators like 'site:' for publisher filtering directly in your query. Examples: query=\\\"artificial intelligence\\\" + when=\\\"w\\\" for past week's AI news query=\\\"climate change\\\" + gl=\\\"us\\\" + hl=\\\"en\\\" for US climate news query=\\\"business news\\\" + when=\\\"d\\\" for today's business news query=\\\"site:bbc.com tesla\\\" + when=\\\"d\\\" for today's BBC Tesla news\",\"input_schema\":{\"type\":\"object\",\"properties\":{\"gl\":{\"type\":\"string\",\"examples\":[\"us\",\"uk\",\"ca\",\"au\",\"de\",\"fr\",\"jp\",\"in\",\"br\",\"mx\"],\"description\":\"Country code for news region (ISO 3166-1 alpha-2). Determines which country's news sources to prioritize.\"},\"hl\":{\"type\":\"string\",\"examples\":[\"en\",\"es\",\"fr\",\"de\",\"pt\",\"it\",\"ja\",\"ko\",\"zh-cn\",\"zh-tw\",\"ar\",\"hi\",\"ru\"],\"description\":\"Language code for news interface and results. Most languages use ISO 639-1 codes (e.g., 'en', 'es'). Chinese requires regional variants: 'zh-cn' (Simplified) or 'zh-tw' (Traditional). Standalone 'zh' is normalized to 'zh-cn'.\"},\"when\":{\"type\":\"string\",\"examples\":[\"d\",\"w\",\"m\",\"y\"],\"description\":\"Time filter for news articles. 'd' = past day, 'w' = past week, 'm' = past month, 'y' = past year. These are coarse UTC-based buckets with no finer granularity; filter `published_at` client-side for precise ranges. Combining narrow queries with strict `when` filters frequently returns zero results; broaden either before concluding no data exists.\"},\"query\":{\"type\":\"string\",\"examples\":[\"artificial intelligence\",\"climate change\",\"site:bbc.com technology\",\"when:7d startup funding\",\"Tesla stock market\",\"COVID-19 vaccine news\"],\"description\":\"Search query for news articles. Supports advanced operators like 'site:', 'when:', etc. Cannot be used with topic_token, publication_token, or story_token.\"},\"start\":{\"type\":\"integer\",\"minimum\":0,\"examples\":[0,10,20,30],\"description\":\"Result offset for pagination. Each page typically contains 10 results. Use multiples of 10 (0, 10, 20, 30, ...) to navigate pages. Stop paginating when a page returns no new results.\"}}},\"hasFullSchema\":true},\"COMPOSIO_SEARCH_WEB\":{\"toolkit\":\"COMPOSIO_SEARCH\",\"tool_slug\":\"COMPOSIO_SEARCH_WEB\",\"description\":\"Perform a web search using the Exa API. Returns a nested structure: narrative summary under results.answer, sources under results.citations (and optionally results.organic_results). Prioritize results.citations as primary evidence over results.answer, which can be vague. Only indexes publicly available content — no paywalled, login-gated, or private content. No date filters enforced; include recency terms in query and verify dates in snippets manually. Throttle to ~1–2 requests/second; bursty queries trigger HTTP 429. Large responses may be stored remotely — use structure_info to locate results.answer and results.citations.\",\"input_schema\":{\"type\":\"object\",\"required\":[\"query\"],\"properties\":{\"query\":{\"type\":\"string\",\"examples\":[\"Coffee\"],\"description\":\"The search query for the Composio Exa API. Must be non-empty; using any other parameter name (e.g., 'q') causes an invalid-request error. Include qualifiers (year, region, platform, intent) for better results — broad queries return generic content; excessive site: or quoted-term filters can return zero results. Add disambiguating terms (city, role, domain) when searching for people or organizations with common names.\"}}},\"hasFullSchema\":true},\"COMPOSIO_SEARCH_FETCH_URL_CONTENT\":{\"toolkit\":\"COMPOSIO_SEARCH\",\"tool_slug\":\"COMPOSIO_SEARCH_FETCH_URL_CONTENT\",\"description\":\"Fetch and extract clean, readable page text (markdown) from public web pages (HTML content) using the Exa API. Use when you need to retrieve actual content from search results or documentation links to extract setup steps, requirements, or citations. Only works with web page URLs - does not support direct links to images, PDFs, or other binary files.\",\"input_schema\":{\"type\":\"object\",\"required\":[\"urls\"],\"properties\":{\"text\":{\"type\":\"boolean\",\"default\":true,\"description\":\"Include extracted markdown text content from the page. Defaults to true.\"},\"urls\":{\"type\":\"array\",\"items\":{\"type\":\"string\"},\"examples\":[[\"https://example.com/article\",\"https://docs.python.org/\"]],\"description\":\"List of public URLs to web pages (HTML content) to fetch content from. URLs must be valid and publicly accessible. Do not use direct links to images (.jpg, .png, .gif), PDFs, or other binary files - use web page URLs only. Also accepts a single URL string.\"},\"extras\":{\"type\":\"object\",\"description\":\"Additional content options like imageLinks or links counts (e.g., {'imageLinks': 3, 'links': 5}).\",\"additionalProperties\":{\"type\":\"integer\"}},\"summary\":{\"anyOf\":[{\"type\":\"boolean\"},{\"type\":\"object\",\"additionalProperties\":{\"type\":\"string\"}}],\"description\":\"Include AI-generated summary of the page content. Can be boolean or object with query/schema options.\"},\"max_characters\":{\"type\":\"integer\",\"description\":\"Maximum number of characters to extract from each page. Maps to text.maxCharacters in Exa API.\"}}},\"hasFullSchema\":true},\"COMPOSIO_SEARCH_TRENDS\":{\"toolkit\":\"COMPOSIO_SEARCH\",\"tool_slug\":\"COMPOSIO_SEARCH_TRENDS\",\"description\":\"Discover trending topics, search patterns, and popularity data. Analyzes search interest over time, ...\",\"hasFullSchema\":false,\"schemaRef\":{\"tool\":\"COMPOSIO_GET_TOOL_SCHEMAS\",\"args\":{\"tool_slugs\":[\"COMPOSIO_SEARCH_TRENDS\"]}}}},\"time_info\":{\"current_time_utc\":\"2026-06-23T16:02:25.531Z\",\"current_time_utc_epoch_seconds\":1782230545,\"message\":\"\\n          - This is time in UTC timezone. Get timezone from user if you needed.\\n          - Always use this time info to construct parameters for tool calls appropriately even when the tool call requires relative times like 'last week', 'last 24 hours', 'today', 'tomorrow' etc.\\n          - Do not hallucinate the time or timezone by yourself.\\n        \"},\"session\":{\"id\":\"ball\",\"generate_id\":false,\"instructions\":\"REQUIRED: Pass session_id \\\"ball\\\" in ALL subsequent meta tool calls for this workflow.\"},\"next_steps_guidance\":[\"1) Connections active, proceed to next step\",\"2) Extract validated plan steps returned above, acknowledge each step, then execute sequentially updating current_step parameter. Check pitfalls during execution.\"],\"success\":true,\"error\":null},\"error\":null,\"log_id\":\"log_MbNAMQO3vExJ\",\"successful\":true}"}],"details":{"mcpServer":"composio","mcpTool":"COMPOSIO_SEARCH_TOOLS"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1782230545578}}
